OL,7,FPaula Vennells says there were
OL,8,Fconcerns at the Post Office over time
OL,9,Fand cost of a review into the
OL,10,Fconvictions of sub-postmasters, ITV
OL,11,FNews' Ellie Pitt reports
OL,13,FA Post Office solicitor was concerned
OL,14,Fthat including former sub-postmistress
OL,15,FSeema Misra's case in an independent
OL,16,Freview into the Horizon IT system
OL,17,F"would be a rag to a bull", the Post
OL,18,FOffice inquiry heard on Thursday.
