OL,7,FMs Misra, who ran a Post Office in
OL,8,FWest Byfleet, Surrey, was jailed in
OL,9,F2010 after being accused of stealing
OL,10,F#74,000. She was eight weeks pregnant
OL,11,Fat the time, and later gave birth to
OL,12,Fher son while wearing an electronic
OL,13,Ftag.
OL,15,FFormer Post Office Chief Executive
OL,16,FPaula Vennells was answering questions
OL,17,Fas part of her second day of evidence
OL,18,Fto the Post Office Inquiry on
OL,19,FThursday, after an and break down in
OL,20,Ftears twice.
