OL,8,Fthe scandal 23 times during her first
OL,9,Fday of evidence, according to the
OL,10,Finquiry's official transcript.
OL,12,FThe inquiry saw an email sent to Ms
OL,13,FVennells in June 2012 expressing
OL,14,Fformer Post Office general counsel
OL,15,FSusan Crichton's concerns about
OL,16,Fincluding Ms Misra's case in the
OL,17,Findependent review.
