OL,7,FThe inquiry was shown an email
OL,8,Fexchange between Ms Vennells and then
OL,9,Fdirector of communications Mark Davies
OL,10,Fin July 2013 in which she said she
OL,11,Fwould "take your steer" after he said
OL,12,Flooking at all past cases would be "in
OL,13,Fmedia terms... very high profile".
OL,15,FMs Vennells agreed that had the Post
OL,16,FOffice decided to review all
OL,17,Fprosecutions of false accounting, it
OL,18,F"may well have" avoided the "lost
OL,19,Fdecade" until miscarriages of justice
OL,20,Finvolving sub-postmasters were
OL,21,Fdiscovered.
